\s1 Introduction to the Sacrificial Regulations
\p 
\v 1 \w Then|strong="H1696"\w* \w the|strong="H3068"\w* \nd \w Lord|strong="H3068"\w*\nd* \w called|strong="H7121"\w* \w to|strong="H1696"\w* \w Moses|strong="H4872"\w* \w and|strong="H4872"\w* \w spoke|strong="H1696"\w* \w to|strong="H1696"\w* \w him|strong="H7121"\w* \w from|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H3068"\w* \w Meeting|strong="H4150"\w* Tent:
